37:01.135 --> 37:03.679
<i>Yogi meditation.</i>

37:03.721 --> 37:05.681
<i>Mm. The Indian kind.</i>

37:05.723 --> 37:06.766
<i>The real deal.</i>

37:06.807 --> 37:08.517
<i>You breathe deep,</i>

37:08.559 --> 37:10.019
<i>let your mind investigate.</i>

37:10.061 --> 37:11.979
<i>Surreal.
