37:33.626 --> 37:35.044
<i>So I'm...</i>

37:35.086 --> 37:37.088
<i>I'm just walking
through the ashes, you know?</i>

37:37.129 --> 37:39.090
<i>I'm breathing and thinking,</i>

37:39.131 --> 37:43.094
<i>just, you know,
