37:55.606 --> 37:57.066
<i>still standing there.</i>

37:57.108 --> 37:59.110
<i>Untouched by the flames.</i>

37:59.151 --> 38:00.611
<i>That's a lucky thing, right?</i>

38:00.653 --> 38:02.530
<i>At least something remains.</i>

