45:19.091 --> 45:20.509
<i>What's he been up to?</i>

45:20.551 --> 45:22.469
<i>I think he's been up to dying.</i>

45:22.511 --> 45:23.887
<i>I read the newspaper,</i>

45:23.929 --> 45:26.014
<i>so I know what's been reported.</i>

45:26.056 --> 45:28.016
<i>Reported about Detective Castellanos.</i>

45:28.058 --> 45:30.018
<i>-Right.
- Got it.</i>

45:30.060 --> 45:31.520
<i>So that's
where you first learned</i>

45:31.562 --> 45:33.021
<i>about Detective Castellanos'
death?</i>

45:33.063 --> 45:34.231
<i>Correct.</i>

45:34.273 --> 45:35.649
<i>Can I ask which newspaper?</i>

45:35.691 --> 45:37.025
<i>Post-Gazette.</i>

45:37.067 --> 45:38.152
<i>You get that delivered?</i>

45:39.194 --> 45:41.071
<i>I live pretty far up
a dirt road,</i>

45:41.113 --> 45:43.198
<i>so I tend to pick it up
when I'm out and about.</i>

45:43.240 --> 45:44.366
<i>Here, in Buell?</i>

45:44.408 --> 45:45.701
<i>That's right.</i>

45:45.743 --> 45:48.829
<i>Or in Brownsville.</i>

46:00.966 --> 46:02.843
<i>low, mysterious music</i>

47:00.359 --> 47:01.860
<i>Internal organ damage,</i>

47:01.902 --> 47:03.487
<i>broken ribs, skull fracture,</i>

47:03.529 --> 47:05.155
<i>-cerebral edema.
- What is that?</i>

47:05.197 --> 47:06.573
<i>Brain swelling.</i>

47:06.615 --> 47:08.534
<i>Your son is in
a medically induced coma</i>

47:08.575 --> 47:10.285
<i>while we monitor him and try
to get the swelling down.</i>

47:10.327 --> 47:13.038
<i>But when it comes down,
he'll be okay?</i>

47:13.080 --> 47:15.040
<i>We hope.
It's still too early to tell</i>

47:15.082 --> 47:17.835
<i>whether he sustained
any long-term brain injuries.</i>

47:18.460 --> 47:21.171
<i>Officer, this is Grace Poe.
She'd like to see her son.</i>

47:22.214 --> 47:24.341
<i>Go ahead.</i>

47:28.929 --> 47:30.681
<i>Is that really necessary?</i>

47:30.722 --> 47:33.350
I'm sorry. It's standard
for prison inmates.

47:33.392 --> 47:34.935
<i>He's not a fucking inmate.</i>

47:36.979 --> 47:39.273
<i>He was awaiting trial.</i>

47:39.314 --> 47:41.733
<i>I'll give you a minute alone.</i>

47:48.198 --> 47:50.158
<i>gentle, somber music</i>

48:05.591 --> 48:07.759
<i>It's okay.</i>

48:13.891 --> 48:16.560
<i>Sweet boy, it's gonna be okay.</i>

48:20.063 --> 48:23.025
<i>You'll be home with me soon.</i>

48:26.194 --> 48:28.071
<i>Just hang on.</i>

48:42.753 --> 48:44.087
<i>Dad?</i>

48:44.129 --> 48:45.756
<i>I'm home.</i>

49:15.577 --> 49:17.329
<i>Are you in there?</i>

49:22.125 --> 49:23.794
<i>Dad?</i>

49:33.720 --> 49:35.681
<i>low, ominous music</i>

49:55.867 --> 49:57.786
<i>Oh, God.</i>

50:24.062 --> 50:25.689
<i>Can I bum one of those?</i>

50:26.606 --> 50:28.025
<i>Yeah.</i>

50:29.067 --> 50:30.610
<i>There you go.</i>

50:39.745 --> 50:41.747
<i>You live here?</i>

50:41.788 --> 50:43.415
<i>Yeah.</i>

50:43.457 --> 50:45.250
<i>Huh.</i>

50:45.292 --> 50:47.252
<i>soft, somber music</i>

50:56.803 --> 50:58.138
<i>You hadn't seen</i>

50:58.180 --> 50:59.306
<i>Detective Castellanos
in a while.</i>

50:59.347 --> 51:00.599
<i>That's right.</i>

51:00.640 --> 51:01.725
<i>How long, you think?</i>

51:01.767 --> 51:04.186
<i>Long time. Close to a decade.</i>

51:04.227 --> 51:05.729
<i>I remember having a beer
with him</i>

51:05.771 --> 51:08.398
<i>maybe six months
after I left Pittsburgh.</i>

51:08.440 --> 51:10.525
<i>-And that was ten years.
- Right.</i>

51:10.567 --> 51:13.361
<i>His recent cell records
show several calls to you.</i>

51:13.403 --> 51:14.571
<i>Do they?</i>

51:14.613 --> 51:17.407
<i>-That's right.
- Interesting.</i>

51:17.449 --> 51:20.410
<i>'Cause I got some calls
from a Pittsburgh number</i>

51:20.452 --> 51:22.162
<i>but never any message.</i>

51:22.204 --> 51:23.413
<i>What was the number?</i>

51:23.455 --> 51:25.582
<i>It just said "Pittsburgh, PA."</i>

51:25.624 --> 51:28.418
<i>If that was Chuck,
you'll see the calls were short.</i>

51:28.460 --> 51:32.964
<i>He must've hung up as soon
as he went to voice mail.</i>

51:34.925 --> 51:37.260
Any idea
what he was calling you about?

51:37.302 --> 51:39.888
<i>Like I said,
he never left a message.</i>

51:41.807 --> 51:43.141
<i>Any guesses?</i>

51:43.183 --> 51:45.602
<i>I don't like to guess.</i>

51:48.313 --> 51:51.316
<i>Gentlemen,
can you excuse me a minute?</i>

52:02.828 --> 52:04.704
<i>low, tense music</i>

52:12.587 --> 52:14.047
<i>Hello, Isaac.</i>

52:14.089 --> 52:15.966
<i>Hi.</i>

52:17.175 --> 52:19.344
<i>You decided to come home.</i>

52:23.974 --> 52:25.934
<i>I have something for you.</i>

52:25.976 --> 52:27.519
<i>All right.</i>

52:50.667 --> 52:52.669
<i>Put it back in your pocket.</i>

52:52.711 --> 52:54.462
<i>Why?</i>

52:56.047 --> 52:57.340
<i>Pick it up.</i>

52:57.382 --> 53:00.051
<i>Put it back in your pocket.</i>

53:01.219 --> 53:03.346
<i>And never show it to anybody.</i>

53:15.483 --> 53:17.444
<i>"You Were Right About
Everything" by Erin McKeown</i>

53:37.881 --> 53:41.218
<i>You were never broken</i>

53:41.259 --> 53:44.387
<i>By ordinary things</i>

53:44.429 --> 53:48.600
<i>You kept holding out</i>

53:48.642 --> 53:51.228
<i>For the big mistake</i>

53:51.269 --> 53:53.563
<i>I was fragile</i>

53:53.605 --> 53:56.775
<i>Too scared and delicate</i>

53:58.610 --> 54:01.071
<i>You kept trying</i>

54:01.112 --> 54:03.782
<i>I'm the one that quit</i>

54:05.575 --> 54:08.161
<i>Worn out by</i>

54:08.203 --> 54:10.580
<i>The baggage that we bring</i>

54:12.916 --> 54:17.754
<i>You were right
about everything</i>
